   462‚Üí
   463‚Üí    >>> delta = dt.timedelta(seconds=3633, days=2, microseconds=123000)
   464‚Üí    >>> precisedelta(delta)
   465‚Üí    '2 days, 1 hour and 33.12 seconds'
   466‚Üí
   467‚Üí    ```
