   470‚Üí    is represented:
   471‚Üí
   472‚Üí    ```pycon
   473‚Üí    >>> precisedelta(delta, format="%0.4f")
   474‚Üí    '2 days, 1 hour and 33.1230 seconds'
   475‚Üí
