   491‚Üí    time of the other units will be adjusted to keep representing the same timedelta:
   492‚Üí
   493‚Üí    ```pycon
   494‚Üí    >>> precisedelta(delta, suppress=['days'])
   495‚Üí    '49 hours and 33.12 seconds'
